        "reasoning": "I integrated the guidance on being specific, using descriptive adjectives, incorporating action, and advising on mood and lighting into the prompt. The headline summarizes the essence of energy harvesting in wearable technology in a succinct and engaging manner suitable for Instagram.",
        "plan": "- Craft a prompt that accurately reflects the content of the Instagram post using DALL-E 3 tips\n- Generate an image for the Instagram post and ensure that it complements the provided text\n- Review the post to ensure it fulfills the objective\n- Send the finished Instagram post to the user",
        "criticism": "I will need to ensure that the resultant image from the prompt aligns with the information in the 'EnergyHarvestingSummary.txt' file and accurately represents the technology in a manner that is understandable to the Instagram audience.",
        "summaryforgpt": "Task: Create an Instagram post on Energy Harvesting for Wearable Technology. Reviewed DALL-E 3 prompt tips and created a detailed visual prompt to generate an Instagram post image. Crafted a headline to use within the image and now executing the 'make_post' command to create the final post."
